OL,3,CShould the Channel Islands trial a
OL,4,Cphone ban in schools?
OL,6,FWith around 200 schools in France
OL,7,Ftrialing a new initiative to ban
OL,8,Fphones for all pupils under 15 during
OL,9,Fthe day, many are wondering whether
OL,10,Fsomething similar could be done across
OL,11,Fthe Channel Islands.
OL,13,FAt Guernsey's Ladies College it is
OL,14,Falready in force and they have not
OL,15,Flooked back.
