OL,3,CShould the Channel Islands trial a
OL,4,Cphone ban in schools?
OL,6,FPrincipal Daniele Harford-Fox says:
OL,7,F"France just published a 140-page
OL,8,Freport, demonstrating the significant
OL,9,Fharms of mobile phone technology, the
OL,10,FSurgeon General in America and the
OL,11,FUK's Education Committee has done the
OL,12,Fsame.
OL,14,F"All of the research overwhelmingly
OL,15,Fshows that this technology is having
OL,16,Fprofound impact on the health and
OL,17,Fwellbeing of our young people and so
OL,18,Fit just remains surprising to me that
OL,19,Fwe aren't acting faster if I'm honest."
