OL,3,CShould the Channel Islands trial a
OL,4,Cphone ban in schools?
OL,6,FIn Kent, one school has given students
OL,7,Fa pouch to put their phones in so they
OL,8,Fcan be locked away during lessons.
OL,10,FThis means the devices do not distract
OL,11,Ffrom learning but can be accessed in
OL,12,Fan emergency and at the end of the
OL,13,Fschool day.
OL,15,FHeadteacher Damien McBeath from The
OL,16,FJohn Wallis Academy says the change
OL,17,Fwas brought in at the start of the
OL,18,Fyear and has been transformational.
