OL,3,CShould the Channel Islands trial a
OL,4,Cphone ban in schools?
OL,6,FHe explains: "It has changed the whole
OL,7,Fculture, we've had a significant
OL,8,Freduction in the number of detentions
OL,9,Fand disruption inside lessons, so in
OL,10,Fterms of behaviour it's shifted
OL,11,Fmassively.
OL,13,F"We've seen a real reduction in
OL,14,Ftruency inside school so children are
OL,15,Fin lessons more than they were. In
OL,16,Fterms of reports of online abuse,
OL,17,Fbullying and misuse of social medi,a
OL,18,Fit's at the lowest it's been in five
OL,19,Fyears."
