OL,3,CShould the Channel Islands trial a
OL,4,Cphone ban in schools?
OL,6,FIn response to questions around an
OL,7,Fisland-wide phone ban in Jersey
OL,8,Fschools, Education Minister Rob Ward
OL,9,Fis not convinced.
OL,11,FHe says: "Yes they can be a
OL,12,Fdistraction but they can also be a
OL,13,Fuseful learning tool and we do have to
OL,14,Feducate our young people on the
OL,15,Fappropriate and sensible use of that
OL,16,Fmobile technology as they grow older,
OL,17,Fso there is a balance to be had here.
OL,18,FI think the majority of our schools do
OL,19,Fit well and that's something we will
OL,20,Fsupport them in as we go forward."
